---
title: Beef Rissoles & Roast Kūmara Chunks with Burger Sauce & Celery Slaw
description: Juicy beef rissoles, crispy roasted kūmara and a crunchy, tangy celery slaw - this meal is packed with flavour! Serve it all with a side of creamy burger sauce for the perfect finishing touch. There you have it - comfort food with a fresh twist!

